## Uso local

```bash
cd advanced-screenshot-agent
python -m venv .venv
source .venv/bin/activate
pip install -e ".[dev]"

screenshot-agent capture --label home-screen --output .vision-runs/demo
screenshot-agent report --run .vision-runs/demo
```

No Windows:

```powershell
cd advanced-screenshot-agent
python -m venv .venv
.\.venv\Scripts\Activate.ps1
pip install -e ".[dev]"
screenshot-agent capture --label home-screen --output .vision-runs/demo
```

